      "title": "Chinese ship visit to Ambantota port - What did India say?",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "Indian Ministry of External Affairs Spokesperson has informed that a Chinese ship is going to visit Ambantota Port.",
        "Arindam Pakshi said that India is closely monitoring any issue that may affect India's security and economic interests and has taken all measures to protect them."
